description:
Etou Minato was a former toji and student of http://anidb.net/ch95151 [Renpu Girls` School]. She was an active toji during the Great Disaster of Sagami Bay, however, much about her career as a toji was put aside when her official records were removed due to unknown reasons.
Source: Toji no Miko Wiki
name: Etou Minato
